    "For the ablation study, each variant processes 85 jailbreak prompts.",
    "They generate 10 jailbreak variants for each.",
    "This approach helps us single out the effect of the components in question.",
    "We repeat the experiment five times.",
    "Then we assess the performances to gauge the omitted impact of each component."
